HYPER + B | Launch Alt Browser
HYPER + LEFT | Swap Window Left (Scrolling)
HYPER + RIGHT | Swap Window Right (Scrolling)
SUPER + Dradle | Toggle Discord Space
SUPER + SHIFT + Dradle | Move To Discord Space
SUPER + SHIFT + ALT + Dradle | Launch Discord
SUPER + Torii | Toggle Media Space
SUPER + SHIFT + Torii | Move To Media Space 
SUPER + SHIFT + ALT + Torii | Launch Spotify
SUPER + Leaf | Toggle Scratchpad
SUPER + SHIFT + Leaf | Move To Scratchpad
SUPER + Soup | Toggle Social Space
SUPER + SHIFT + Soup | Move To Social Space 
SUPER + SHIFT + ALT + Soup | Launch Instagram
SUPER + CTRL + ALT + Soup | Launch TikTok
SUPER + LMB | Move Window
SUPER + RMB | Resize Window
CTRL ALT + SCROLL UP | Zoom In
CTRL ALT + SCROLL DOWN | Zoom Out
SHIFT + ALT + SCROLL | Reset Zoom
SUPER + Scroll | Change Workspace
Press Knob | Mute Audio
Hold Knob | Audio Menu
[TMUX] CTRL + ALT + Left | Close Terminal Pane
[TMUX] CTRL + ALT + Right | Split Terminal Right
[TMUX] CTRL + ALT + Down | Split Terminal Down 
[TMUX] CTRL + A | <PREFIX>
