[TMUX] ALT + O | New Terminal Window (Home Dir)
[TMUX] CTRL + Left | Focus Pane Left
[TMUX] CTRL + Right | Focus Pane Right
[TMUX] CTRL + Up | Focus Pane Above
[TMUX] CTRL + Down | Focus Pane Below
